data.description: Nestled on just over an acre of land in a prime location, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom cottage home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. The property is strategically situated close to the interstate, ensuring an easy commute for residents. There is an 8x16 shed providing additional storage, the generous land space invites endless possibilities for customization. Whether you dream of adding on to the existing structure, constructing a workshop, parking a boat or RV, installing a pool, or cultivating your own lush vegetable gardens, this property provides the canvas for your ideal home and lifestyle. Embrace the freedom to tailor this idyllic space to suit your unique vision and enjoy the harmonious balance of country living with urban accessibility.
